Company Overview of Trian Fund Management, L.P.



SnapshotPeople 




OverviewBoard MembersCommittees



Executive Profile
Matthew H. Peltz  Partner and Senior Analyst, Trian Fund Management, L.P.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 2 Board Members in 2 different organizations across 3 different industries.See Board Relationships34--
Background

		Mr. Matthew H. Peltz serves as the Partner and Senior Analyst at Trian Fund Management, L.P. Mr. Peltz has been a member of the Investment Team at the firm since January 2008. As a senior member of the Investment Team, he sources new investment ideas, leads due diligence on potential investments and focuses on portfolio construction, risk management and corporate governance matters. Mr. Peltz served at The Goldman Sachs Group, Inc. from May 2006 to January 2008, as an ... Investment Banking Analyst. He has been Director of The Wendy's Company since December 14, 2015. Mr. Peltz serves as a Member of the Andover Development Board at Phillips Academy. He served as a Director of ARG Holdings, Inc., from September 2012 to December 2015. Mr. Peltz has received a B.A. from Yale University in the year 2006.Read Full Background




