                                                    BRIEF-The Wendy's Company announces addition to board
                                                


                                                    Reuters – 
                                                    9:17 AM ET 07/20/2017
                                                


Wendys Co. * The Wendy's Company (WEN) announces addition of Kristin A. Dolan to board of directors. * Wendys Co - ‍board of directors has increased size of board from 11 to 12 members​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:

















                                                    The Wendy's Company Announces Addition of Kristin A. Dolan to Board of Directors
                                                


                                                    PR Newswire – 
                                                    9:00 AM ET 07/20/2017
                                                


DUBLIN, Ohio, July 20, 2017 The Wendy's Company  today announced that on July 19, 2017, its Board of Directors has increased the size of the Board from 11 to 12 members and elected Kristin A. Dolan to serve as a director of the Company, effective immediately. November 2016.

















                                                    Wendy's Treats Pitchfork Music Festival Fans to a Re-Freshing Experience
                                                


                                                    PR Newswire – 
                                                    4:34 PM ET 07/15/2017
                                                


CHICAGO, July 15, 2017  Wendy's (WEN) kept it fresh at the Pitchfork Music Festival all weekend. About The Wendy's Company The Wendy's Company (WEN) is the world's third largest quick-service hamburger restaurant chain.

















                                                    Wendy's Has Found a Cure for Your Queso Obsession
                                                


                                                    PR Newswire – 
                                                    8:00 AM ET 07/11/2017
                                                


DUBLIN, Ohio, July 11, 2017  Wendy's® knows how passionate people have become about queso. Kurt Kane. "Nobody does fresh beef, chicken sandwiches and topped fries like Wendy's (WEN), so we've taken three things our customers already love and made them even better by adding queso."

















                                                    The Wendy's Company to Report 2017 Second Quarter Results on Wednesday, August 9
                                                


                                                    PR Newswire – 
                                                    4:05 PM ET 07/10/2017
                                                


DUBLIN, Ohio, July 10, 2017  The Wendy's Company (WEN) will release its second quarter 2017 results before the market opens on Wednesday, August 9. A conference call will follow at 9 a.m. ET, with a simultaneous webcast from the investors section of the Company's website at www.aboutwendys.com. The live conference call will be available at 572-6014 or, for international callers, at 913-8524.

















                                                    Parent of Burger King, Tim Hortons to curb antibiotics in chicken
                                                


                                                    Reuters – 
                                                    11:36 AM ET 06/22/2017
                                                


The parent of Burger King and Tim Hortons on Thursday vowed to cut the use of antibiotics in its chicken supply, joining other major fast-food chain operators in the battle against the rise of dangerous antibiotic-resistant bacteria known as superbugs.

















