Director of Wendy’sny  (NASDAQ:WEN), Peltz Matthew H., sells 5,500,000 shares worth $87,835,000
According to Wendy'sny 's most recent Form 4 filing with the SEC dated Jun 07 05:10 PM, company Director, Peltz Matthew H. disclosed selling 5,500,000 shares at a cost of $15.97. At the time of this transaction (Jun 05), this trade was worth $87,835,000 in total. As of Jun 05, Peltz Matthew H. now owns 39,035,921 shares in total worth about $621,842,221.53. 
