Sport 



Technical gear for sport climbing and ice climbing, but also aid climbing, mountaineering, caving, via ferrata, multi-pitch climbing, canyoning… Headlamps for climbing, trail running, sailing, fishing or any pursuit that requires hands-free lighting.






Professional 



Equipment for work-at-height and rescue professionals: fall arrest, work positioning, personal escape, difficult to access and confined space rescue systems. Specialized headlamps for professionals.
















Access the inaccessiblePetzl's mission is to create innovative solutions, tools or services, that help people progress in vertical or dark environments.
More info 





The Petzl GroupDiscover our history, our know-how, our expertise, key figures, and our job offers.
More info 





Petzl SolutionsA longside the distribution network, Petzl has developed a parallel network, Petzl Solutions, with a desire to diffuse and to share complementary information and educational modules.
More info 





Petzl FoundationThe Petzl Foundation supports educational, environmental and research initiatives all over the world. Visit their website to learn more about their projects.
